The,World,Bank,Climate,Change,Knowledge,Portal,offers,information,reports,and,data,about,climate,and,climate,change,The,World,Bank,Climate,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,data,from,the,Climate,Change,Knowledge,Portal,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,searching,and,returning,climate,data,points,such,as,average,temperatures,and,rainfalls,and,changes,in,averages,and,by,countries